Directory structure
===================

(Same directory structure as [[file:../sim_4d_vlasov_poisson_PIC_cartesian]])

   test_4d_vp_lt_pic_cartesian   -- executable
   params_lt_pic_4d.nml          -- input file
   README                        -- info (this file)
   run/                          -- output directory

HOWTO
=====

Source location:
        [[file:simulation_4d_vp_lt_pic_cartesian.F90]]
	[[file:unit_test_4d_vp_lt_pic_cartesian.F90]]
	
Parameter file:
	[[file:params_lt_pic_4d.nml]]
	[[file:../../../../usr/simulations/simulations_parallel/4d_vp_pic_cartesian/params_lt_pic_4d.nml]]

Configuring:
	[[elisp:(compile "cd ../../../../build && cmake -DHDF5_PARALLEL_ENABLED=ON -DCMAKE_VERBOSE_MAKEFILE=TRUE ../src")]]

	(note: [[file:../CMakeLists.txt]] has a list of required features for activating parallel tests)
	
Compiling:

	First complete initial make (to solve missing dependencies issues)
		[[elisp:(compile "cd ../../../../build && make")]]

	Next makes
		[[elisp:(compile "cd ../../../../build && make test_4d_vp_lt_pic_cartesian && make install")]]

Running:
	- Create output directory if missing, and move into it
	     $ mkdir run
	     $ cd run

	     [[elisp:(compile "mkdir ../../../../usr/simulations/simulations_parallel/4d_vp_pic_cartesian/run")]]

	- Run parallel simulation within directory
	     $ mpirun -np 4 ../test_4d_vp_pic_cartesian ../params_pic_4d.nml

	     [[elisp:(compile "cd ../../../../usr/simulations/simulations_parallel/4d_vp_pic_cartesian/run && mpirun -np 4 ../test_4d_vp_lt_pic_cartesian ../params_lt_pic_4d.nml)]]

	- Run gnuplot script generated at runtime
	     $ gnuplot --persist rho_init.gnu

Ctest:
	[[elisp:(compile "cd ../../build && ctest -R 4d_vp_lt_pic_cartesian")]]

clean:
	[[elisp:(compile "cd ../../../../build && make clean")]]

